@startuml
title US14 - SSD - View Appointment Details

autoactivate on
autonumber

actor "User"
participant ":RestAPI" as System

activate User

User -> System : GET /api/appointments/{appointmentId}
System --> User : 200 OK (AppointmentDTO)
alt Not authenticated or forbidden
    System --> User : 403 Forbidden
else Appointment not found
    System --> User : 404 Not Found
end

note right of System
- Administrator: Can view any appointment.
- Patient: Can only view their own appointments.
end note

@enduml
